Package: kRypto
Title: Pull Cryptocurrency Data in Tidy Format Form Coinmarketcap API
Version: 1.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Adelmo",
           family = "Filho",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "adelmo.aguiar.filho@gmail.com")
Description: A wrapper for pulling cryptocurrency data in tidy format form 'Coinmarketcap' API <https://api.coinmarketcap.com> associated with web scraping tools. By automatically batching API requests, it allows you to enter an cryptocurrency's name and retrieve their current or historical data.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: R (>= 3.4)
Suggests: 
    covr,
    testthat
Imports: 
    stringi,
    xml2,
    rvest,
    dplyr,
    purrr,
    stringr,
    httr,
    lubridate
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
URL: https://github.com/adelmofilho/kRypto
